 result←object value arg
⍝ Allow reading and setting the list of highlighted items
⍝ This is not managed with a variable but reads and writes the object property directly

 :If 0=≢arg
     result←⍸object ##.##.∆WG'SelItems'
 :Else
     object ##.##.∆WS'SelItems'((⍳≢object ##.##.∆WG'Items')∊∊##.##.Single arg) ⍝ Write the new value directly to Dyalog
     result←##.NoRes
 :EndIf
